Body: Bitcoin Garden: New opportunities are open for influencers https://bitcoingarden.org/new-opportunities-are-open-for-influencers/  The consumption of digital content is growing day by day. That is why brands and companies increase their expenses on digital marketing. For ads, however, it is becoming increasingly difficult to reach their goal and come under public notice. Users actively apply ad-blockers to hide annoying ads. According to the Statista data, ad blocking user penetration rate in the USA grew from 15.7% in 2014 to 27.5% in 2017. This figure is expected to rise to 30.1 percent in 2018.  The Linqia‚Äôs report on the State of Influencer Marketing 2018 shows that 39% of marketers plan to increase influencer marketing budgets in 2018. It means that brands are looking for new ways to advertise their goods and services more and more recognizing the advantages of influencer marketing tools. The explosive growth in such social media as YouTube, Facebook, Instagram, and Twitter changed the marketing model and attracted a great number of advertisers. The brands and companies actively cooperate with influencers so that they use brands and companies‚Äô products in their content because they have a huge number of followers, who consider the influencers‚Äô opinion.  The influencer marketing has been used in the entertainment industry for years until the large companies engaged in other branches appreciated its value. Even small companies are interested in the cooperation with popular bloggers influencing the choice of potential consumers. In contrast to usual advertisements, influencers enjoy users‚Äô confidence and attention. According to the marketers, about 75% of users look for information about new brands and products in social media and a half of them rely on influencers when deciding on the purchase....

Its global digital assets service platform operates from GBC high-tech industrial complex in Ulaanbaatar. The platform is designed to be trustworthy and user-friendly cryptocurrency exchange and has many useful functions as multi-language support service, and multi-level security architect that ensures a safe transaction of digital asset exchange and Android App providing the same features for the most mobile traders. Since PATRON platform could supply a transparent business skim by making the market tokenized and implementing blockchain technology into its digital core, sponsors can cut a significant amount of commission fee that used to be paid to agencies, and influencers can get more opportunities. Author: PATRON ICO
Title: [ANN - ICO] <<<PATRON>>> Japan's Influencer Service <<<LIVE>>>
Body: Influencers and SNS users from around the world can publish, discover, reserve, or sell inflationary the information of ‚Äúsocial network media sharing economy‚Äù about acquisition / PR ambassador matching, on the Internet, mobile phone or tablet. PATRON (Patron) is a highly reliable marketplace that can deliver all at once to LIVE.   VIDEO | WEBSITE | TELEGRAM | WHITE PAPER | AIRDROP | LINKEDIN  <<<TEST OUR BETTA>>>  What Is Patron? The company has its roots in Japan and is a project that incorporates the current trends associated with cryptocurrency and other communities online. It‚Äôs widely influenced by social media. Patron plans to tokenize the social media influenced aspect of the internet to help connect brands with the appropriate influencers.  Patron is attempting to capitalize on these relationships, but not before bringing influencer and product together. Popular accounts on social media are well known to collaborate with different brands in order to represent them and provide massive amounts of exposure.  They want to help them get as much business as possible and brand themselves to develop their brand further. It will enable influencers with the ability to connect with more brands through Patron online and on mobile.   How Patron Influencer Social Media Blockchain Token Rewards Works  Patron has a few major functions:  The project ultimately wants to create next-level services for any new influencers as well as give them a platform for equality.  ‚ÄúWe want to make a global impact on the level of Apple and Google and bring Japan‚Äôs thriving tech and influencer scene to new markets. Over the past four years we have worked with influencers and social media. We have the network built, the experience, and the technological expertise to make this dream a reality.‚Äù  A lot of people may wonder what the benefits of using Patron are? As of now, they claim that SNS marketing fees are somewhere in the realm of 40% worldwide. The project wants to use smart contracts like on Ethereum to help eliminate any brokerage fees. It will allow influencers the ability to decrease the amount of payments given to clients.    Patron ICO Details  Start Date ‚Äì March 26, 2018 End Date ‚Äì April 27, 2018 22:30 UTC  Total tokens issued: 400,000,000 PAT Token sales: 240,000,000 PAT  Token PAT Price 1 PAT = 0.14 - 0. 50 USD Bonus Available Platform Ethereum Accepting ETH, BTC, LTC, Various Minimum investment 0.01ETH, 0.01 BTC Soft cap 4,000,000 USD Hard cap 35,000,000 USD Country Japan Whitelist/KYC KYC  Visit our website for more details or join our community     Funding for project has been divided into several different areas:   Product Development: Any products on the platform will be available on DAPPs and Mobile. Also, the cost of development for the influencer complex platform will be incorporated into this. As well any expenses, resource acquisition, marketing and advertising as well.  Global Expansion: We also plans to establish ourself deep in the heart of Silicon Valley.  Toyo Influencer Hub: At this section, funding goes to influencers and finding new influencers for the future as well as engineers, marketers and advertisers in Tokyo. The hub is even promised to include a movie studio and workspace.   The technical specs of Patron are as follows:  - Coin is cryptocurrency of an open-sourced nature - PAT is implemented on the Public Ethereum Blockchain as an ERC20 token - PAT is new standard for common currency that will be used with Patron‚Äôs Ecosystem - Patron coin distribution is said to release 240 million coins during the ICO. This is out of the total 400 million coins. 160 million of the PAT is said to be allocated to --  Patron and is then used for distribution or to the various members of the board for Patron.     Who Is Behind Patron?   CEO ‚Äì Atsushi Hisatumi. He is the leader of the entire project and is one of the largest influencer advocates in Japan.  CTO is Mutsumi Ishihara | CCO is Terry Shiraishi | CMO is Kosuke Takada | CFO is Satoshi Fukudome Please find many more people on the website
